        <li data-list-text="3.">
            <p style="
            padding-left: 41pt;
            text-indent: -18pt;
            line-height: 108%;
            text-align: justify;
          ">
                    I state that <u>{{data.sonof}}</u> (as appearing on the share
                    certificate) was also known as <u>{{data.deceasedholdername}}</u> (name as
                appearing on the death certificate) and that both names belong to one
                and the same person.
            </p>
        </li>
        <li data-list-text="4.">
            <p style="
            padding-left: 41pt;
            text-indent: -18pt;
            line-height: 15pt;
